name: Set of all sets #1/3
description:
What is my reference point? 

I don't see my feet,

I only see peaks, they're like lighthouses.

Useless, they are dazzling me.

I take sections, sections of a whole, 
different from each other and difficult to understand.

I can't see but I need it to get there.

I alone cannot put these pieces together.

Maybe if I'm closer to them I can turn them off.

The terrain becomes complicated. 

It doesn't help not being able to see.

I get lost in the depths.

I'd like to see more...

Down, here.

by Rotten_ttc
